BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Earth Day Ride in North York
DTSTART:20250426T140000Z
DTEND:20250426T153000Z
DTSTAMP:20250424T210048Z
UID:02531c17-c594-5665-adf4-894676eeeb0a
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a leisurely 9km ride around North York to explore 
 some local streets and the unfolding story about planned changes to make Y
 onge Street more people-friendly. Meet at the parkette at the corner of Yo
 nge Street and Park Home Avenue (in front of Aroma Espresso\, one block no
 rth of the North York Civic Centre). If arriving from outside North York\,
  consider taking the TTC and renting a Bike Share bike nearby. (https://ww
 w.facebook.com/events/526071400571287/?post_id=528408233670937&view=permal
 ink&notif_id=1745329422975867&notif_t=feedback_reaction_generic&ref=notif)
