UID:ce7858b4-8853-5987-a6c1-34270e9e30a9
DESCRIPTION:Jane's Walk event on Sunday\, May 4 at 10am (ending at about 1
 1:30am). Start point NE corner of Bloor Street and Brunswick Ave. Total wa
 lk distance: 1.5km. Hosted by Eric Kamphof\, Pedaal Coffee + Bikes and Alb
 ert Koehl\, Coordinator\, Community Bikeways. Learn about the desirable pr
 oliferation of e-bikes on city streets\, and work that needs to be done by
  governments to regulate the growing size\, weight and power of some e-bik
 es. Free. Family-friendly. No registration required.\n\n#block-1680391a3c6
 dafe87424 { --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px\; --tweak-text-bloc
